# get_irida_analysis_queue
# get the current analysis queue status (running and queued counts)
#
# This uses the undocumented AJAX endpoint GET /ajax/analyses/queue which
# returns running and queued analysis counts without querying Galaxy.
# Unlike the REST API analysis endpoints, this is lightweight and safe to poll.
#
# AJAX endpoints require session auth (JSESSIONID cookie), not Bearer token.
# This function logs in via POST /login, stores the session cookie in a
# temporary file, and uses it for the AJAX call.
#
# usage: get_irida_analysis_queue
#
# example: get_irida_analysis_queue
